{"tid":36172,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲個頭長期好lup?","createTime":"2016-12-12T13:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T06:34:14.000Z","uid":28716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f14aca04f076d5dd69f85ab261eca3d0cc9c6b73","tid":36172,"uid":28716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:53:40.000Z","msg":"即係咁 我由小學開始就習慣每朝起身都會洗頭沖涼<br />\n一來個人真係會精神啲(感覺上) 二來本身頭髮比較硬 瞓醒會豎起晒好柒<br />\n但呢幾年就發現每日去到五六點 就算冇乜點出汗 個頭都開始好Lup 又油油地<br />\n另外就算臨瞓前洗咗頭 第二朝又係好撚Lup <br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時摸下個頭仲會有啲臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 冇gel頭 身邊嘅人唔洗頭都唔會Lup 奇撚怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b969aed147fe49d0326da3f2a93cfe154da894d8","tid":36172,"uid":13850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"轉洗頭水"},{"pid":"f354107c5751676437d79101cfe7b1ebf2836c05","tid":36172,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:58:04.000Z","msg":"𣲷"},{"pid":"863c15334dda91e53cf3bfd805fb0bfa3cc74482","tid":36172,"uid":28716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉洗頭水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n髮型師都有講過 話藥房有得賣嘅都係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n斷估唔會個個都咁捨得買貴洗頭水嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f4aeaeafaddd11fa34052e54795ad624881154","tid":36172,"uid":13850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>轉洗頭水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n髮型師都有講過 話藥房有得賣嘅都係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n斷估唔會個個都咁捨得買貴洗頭水嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係絲，唔係太識男人用洗頭水"},{"pid":"861c89b58aae5eb83c93bd09490fafaef2fc04dd","tid":36172,"uid":13850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB