":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:12:14.000Z","msg":"要用deep clean<br />\n愈係無色透明果d就好<br />\n千祈唔好用好潤果d<br />\n愈用愈油"},{"pid":"49f9e7b470befe514752a52a77c42836f3cff70f","tid":36172,"uid":17414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"識人好似你咁 試過神早上佢屋企佢岩岩起身未洗頭 個頭望落油到好似岩岩洗完頭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後佢洗頭既時候落兩次洗頭水 就變到無咁油 唔知關唔關事 個可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b674375e455b4b94f2c3642085b78b853d554417","tid":36172,"uid":28716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要用deep clean<br />\n愈係無色透明果d就好<br />\n千祈唔好用好潤果d<br />\n愈用愈油</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頂 仲以為寫住深層滋潤係好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f457d4c7f08c4c113763312695d812408f2ce9","tid":36172,"uid":28716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識人好似你咁 試過神早上佢屋企佢岩岩起身未洗頭 個頭望落油到好似岩岩洗完頭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後佢洗頭既時候落兩次洗頭水 就變到無咁油 唔知關唔關事 個可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又未油到呢個地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會轉洗頭水！"},{"pid":"b93ea8921446e959db887435e575340ff811d502","tid":36172,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:36:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識人好似你咁 試過神早上佢屋企佢岩岩起身未洗頭 個頭望落油到好似岩岩洗完頭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後佢洗頭既時候落兩次洗頭水 就變到無咁油 唔知關唔關事 個可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個頭唔算油，但慣咗隔個禮拜一次過洗兩次<br />\n個感覺真係完全唔同<br />\n洗第二次嗰時feel到真係洗梗頭皮，洗完會覺得好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2fc64e532cbaab5997aacb1e16bc1fbfd4daeb","tid":36172,"uid":36744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有無咩牌子嘅洗頭水好推介？"}]}